1. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper analyzes the error probability of a wireless communication system, which is a core topic in information theory. 
2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses a cooperative wireless communication system, which is a key aspect of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper considers power consumption sources beyond data transmission power, which is related to system and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper mentions wireless information transmission (WIT), which is related to multimedia. 
5. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper uses numerical results to show the importance of cooperation, which involves computational engineering.
